# ─── Build artifacts ──────────────────────────────────────────────
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/target
**/.angular
**/build

# ─── IDE / OS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.idea
.vscode
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# ─── VCS ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.git
.gitignore
.gitattributes

# ─── Logs ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/*.log
**/npm-debug.log*
**/yarn-debug.log*
**/yarn-error.log*

# ─── Test & coverage output ───────────────────────────────────────
**/coverage
**/.nyc_output
**/test-results
**/playwright-report

# ─── Local env / secrets ──────────────────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
**/application-local.properties

# ─── Docs (not needed at build time — speeds up context upload) ──
README.md
SETUP.md
RENDER_DEPLOYMENT.md
HELP.md
STARTUP_GUIDE.md
*.postman_collection.json

# ─── Docker meta itself ──────────────────────────────────────────
Dockerfile
.dockerignore
docker-compose*.yml
